trans-unit.source: Defines the contract that associates incoming messages with a local operation to customize service execution behavior.
trans-unit.target: 定义将传入消息与本地操作来自定义服务执行行为相关联的协定。

trans-unit.source: Implement and insert a custom operation selector to customize the selection of the operation to which an incoming message is dispatched in a service application.
trans-unit.target: 实现并插入自定义操作选择器，自定义服务应用程序中，传入消息调度到操作的所选内容。

trans-unit.source: Assign the IDispatchOperationSelector object to the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.DispatchRuntime.OperationSelector%2A> property to insert the custom selector.
trans-unit.target: IDispatchOperationSelector 将对象分配给<xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.DispatchRuntime.OperationSelector%2A>属性插入自定义选择器。</xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.DispatchRuntime.OperationSelector%2A>

trans-unit.source: Associates a local operation with the incoming method.
trans-unit.target: 将本地操作与传入的方法相关联。

trans-unit.source: The incoming <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.Message> to be associated with an operation.
The name of the operation to be associated with the message.
trans-unit.target: 要与之关联的操作的名称 message 。
